<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: amountVested(tokenId) - grants[tokenId].amountRedeemed [2836,2890]" label="amountVested(tokenId) + grants[tokenId].amountRedeemed" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: block.timestamp < grants[tokenId].cliffTimestamp [3229,3277]" label="block.timestamp <= grants[tokenId].cliffTimestamp" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: ((uint128(block.timestamp) - grants[tokenId].startTimestamp) / grants[tokenId].vestInterval) * grants[tokenId].vestAmount [3464,3585]" label="((uint128(block.timestamp) + grants[tokenId].startTimestamp) + grants[tokenId].vestInterval) + grants[tokenId].vestAmount" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: amount > grants[tokenId].totalAmount [3666,3702]" label="amount >=  grants[tokenId].totalAmount" />
  <update-node tree="comparison_operator: == [1136,1138]" label="<=" />
  <update-node tree="comparison_operator: > [1263,1264]" label=">=" />
  <update-node tree="comparison_operator: >= [1443,1445]" label=">" />
</actions>
